title: Pages are an outdated version until refreshing.
content:
Hi there, For a couple of weeks my youtube.com and myanimelist.net have both been outdated versions of the sites, such as my youtube showing recommendations i saw weeks ago and my myanimelist showing my shows as unwatched or at an outdated amount of episodes watched. It only changes back to up to date when i refresh.

I have tried clearing my cache and booting in safe mode and these both didn't work. This issue isn't that pressing but getting it fixed would be amazing. I couldn't find anything in the help forums or on google or reddit so Im asking here.
creator: harveyscott9898

title: Old Firefox Account
content: My husband bought a new computer and signed into Firefox with the wrong email but the right password. Needless to say his decades of info disappeared. I have the recovery key from his old computer, am I guaranteed it will recover his old info? He is so sure it will fail he just wants to return the new machine and struggle with the crappy old one.

title: Edits using the clipboard not working with Google apps.
content: Copy, Cut and Paste are not working in Google Sheets or Google Docs using Ctrl-X, Ctrl-C or Ctrl-V. Other control combos do work such as Ctrl-Z, Y and F. These features are working on Chrome with the same files. I disabled extensions and tried the Troubleshoot mode. Neither helped. Using Firefox desktop 138.0.1 on Win-10 Pro.
